{"type": "article", "id": 26603, "title": "螺旋灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-10T06:52:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 93, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702151939LAcMnh6vV5kW2rpa.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">光是直线传播的，不过 Andrii Kovalskyi 设计的这一系列名为 Spiral 的螺旋状的吊灯和壁灯则提供了一个新的启发。高科技的 LED 灯带有着很高的灵活度，同薄木条结合后像是有一双无形的手在空中挥舞着光的束带。虽然整体造型有点过于华丽了，但这样的灯具的确能为房间增色不少。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151936dRhXokJCGjY9SO8W.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151937vLZ2N0kA5rSVB9QG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151937Db5Waw702ECkIrd4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021519385gyZn8POhsztS4qf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}